    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. Uncertainty quantification has been completed with Monte Carlo propagation of inlet flow and rotational speed variability, confirming NIH predictions remain below RH = 1 threshold across the sampled input space. The 13-factor credibility profile supports acceptance of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in the CPB COU.",
